description.narrative: In informal settlements, UNICEF provided access to temporary safe drinking water supply to 208,226 refugees and sanitation services to over 202,734 refuges. At the stabilization front, UNICEF provided improved access to sustainable drinking water services to over 350,602 people and improved access to sustainable wastewater services to nearly 379,311 people. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/01/2020
